        <mj-image border-radius="10px" padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.presidentialsummary.com/email/images/olivia-grant-hugs-grandmother-mary-grace-sileo-plastic-cloth-wantagh-new-york.png" alt="Olivia Grant hugs her grandmother, Mary Grace Sileo, through a plastic cloth hung on a clothesline in Wantagh, New York" href="https://www.presidentialsummary.com" />
